      "Key": "0614BEF94A92B30D564FFDA004913790",
      "SourceString": "Add to a weapon's Relic Slot while crafting to deal ELEMENTAL ICE damage and use the ICE Storm ability. Strong against FIRE.\n\nICE Storm - Charge your weapon by dealing damage. When fully charged, use <keybind touch_img=\"ICEStorm\">Target</> to create an ICY storm, dealing some damage, but rapidly building up ELEMENTAL Affliction.",
